{"tid":1278711,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連何韻詩都會進步， 泛民幾時可以進步下","createTime":"2019-07-02T13:43:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T03:36:51.000Z","uid":43785,"like":541,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":65,"replies":[{"pid":"8a3b6304f0e023b9fc63e3654f5546074c5999b3","tid":1278711,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T13:43:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cVLCFAx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcVLCFAx.jpg&h=5356999f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n連何韻詩都會進步， 泛民幾時可以進步下<br />\n<br />\n尋日白頭佬 張超雄呢D人， 真係睇見都有啲眼冤， 有時唔係話想分化， 但有時候人真係要進步， 你唔可以對有思想嘅示威者咁樣做， 咁樣變相係協助極權管治香港。<br />\n<br />\n算啦，希望大家真係要進步， 我地唔會同抗爭者嗰割席， 全力支持願意為香港付出抗爭嘅人，唔好違抗爭者拖後腿。<br />\n <br />\n唔該各位泛民議員，要進步喇各位！<br />\n<br />\n你唔願意為香港做英雄， 都唔好阻住英雄去做佢哋要做嘅事。"},{"pid":"73b9f76f1361f913192f3b62857543faa13785a8","tid":1278711,"uid":43785,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T14:46:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcc292c7c3c3aaa215fe80339259ed18fc5fb51d","tid":1278711,"uid":11948,"like":229,"dislike":1,"score":228,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T14:47:48.000Z","msg":"泛民都有部分進化，係白頭佬on9啫"},{"pid":"53c3c26262774d195b2f571a78568b595edac1b7","tid":1278711,"uid":21545,"like":103,"dislike":3,"score":100,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T14:54:34.000Z","msg":"關爸爸咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢成晚都喺立法會入面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54f886033d27444333740f4f41e1463763025acf","tid":1278711,"uid":71377,"like":38,"dislike":1,"score":37,"quote":{"pid":"53c3c26262774d195b2f5