想提黃毓民條撚屌， 所以熱血公民當年反黃毓民，我係支持嘅。<br />\n所以當年先有人誤會我係熱狗， 我從來都唔係熱狗亦都冇加入個熱狗呢個組織。"},{"pid":"bcd791cc2d21490d88617ad52b882bb4349f90cf","tid":1278711,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T00:43:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ad9c25b768affa31d911d755a08f72a4790936f","tid":1278711,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T00:50:44.000Z","msg":"其實係文化監暴令佢以前乜都唔敢講"},{"pid":"2033a5f4e751d8b491c7265a87367366ca8ba05b","tid":1278711,"uid":43785,"like":9,"dislike":4,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"0ad9c25b768affa31d911d755a08f72a4790936f","tid":1278711,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T00:50:44.000Z","msg":"其實係文化監暴令佢以前乜都唔敢講"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T00:54:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大佬呀<br />\n譴責抗爭者， 何韻詩以前咁樣講果陣，<br />\n我屌撚到仆街冚家剷。<br />\n<br />\n依家進步咗其實我希望佢真係要同抗爭者黎個道歉。 依家明顯係冇成本轉軚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過好多人都覺得冇乜問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁我唯有當係冇問題啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 全世界叫原諒佢我咪原諒佢囉。<br />\n但係班老泛民唔該醒少少啦， 何韻詩都識轉軚你哋點解仲未轉"},{"pid":"9b1142af1563bd28ef105e1af235e0f7103970de","tid":1278711,"uid":35014,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T00:55:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"db4bd19536cae906175e5a92d825c686a37fd905","tid":1278711,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9b1142af1563bd28ef105e1af235e0f7103970de","tid":1278711,"uid":35014,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T00:55:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T05:59:22.000Z","ms